  <title>DOW-UAP-PR068, IIR 1 666 S0151 23/Video Footage of Unidentified Aerial Phenomenon (UAP) captured by fifth generation aircraft on 20 Jan 23</title>
  <originaltitle>200123-D-D0360-3203</originaltitle>
